txt.en: Helegrod was once an outpost of the great dwarf-realm of the Misty Mountains known to most as Moria. Giants under the influence of Skorgrím Dourhand and the Angmarim now call this wing of the dwarf-hold home.
Complete Giants in the Service of Angmar
The mighty Storvâgûn leads his people in the fastness of Helegrod, holding the fortress against the Free Peoples.
